{"tag":"section","attrib":{"id":"id0dfbcdd2-3a70-11f1-a648-bee82ed8a795","identifier":"/us/usc/t20/s6052"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"6052"},"text":"§ 6052.","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":" Continuation of awards","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"subsection","attrib":{"id":"id0dfbcdd3-3a70-11f1-a648-bee82ed8a795","identifier":"/us/usc/t20/s6052/a"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"a"},"text":"(a)","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":" In general","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"chapeau","attrib":{},"text":"Notwithstanding any other provision of law, from funds appropriated under subsection (b), the Secretary—","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"paragraph","attrib":{"id":"id0dfbcdd4-3a70-11f1-a648-bee82ed8a795","identifier":"/us/usc/t20/s6052/a/1"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"1"},"text":"(1)","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"content","attrib":{},"text":" shall continue to fund any multiyear grant or contract awarded under section 3141 and parts A and C of title XIII of the Elementary and Secondary Education Act of 1965 (as such provisions were in effect on the day preceding ","children":[{"tag":"date","attrib":{"date":"2002-01-08"},"text":"January 8, 2002","children":[],"tail":"), for the duration of that multiyear award in accordance with its terms; and"}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"paragraph","attrib":{"id":"id0dfbcdd5-3a70-11f1-a648-bee82ed8a795","identifier":"/us/usc/t20/s6052/a/2"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"2"},"text":"(2)","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"content","attrib":{},"text":" may extend, on a year-to-year basis, any multiyear grant or contract awarded under an authority described in paragraph (1) that expires after ","children":[{"tag":"date","attrib":{"date":"2002-01-08"},"text":"January 8, 2002","children":[],"tail":", but before the enactment of successor authority to this subchapter."},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"idref":"fn002194"},"text":"1","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"note","attrib":{"type":"footnote","id":"fn002194"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{},"text":"1","children":[],"tail":" See References in Text note below."}],"tail":null}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"subsection","attrib":{"id":"id0dfbcdd6-3a70-11f1-a648-bee82ed8a795","identifier":"/us/usc/t20/s6052/b"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"b"},"text":"(b)","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":" Authorization of appropriations","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"content","attrib":{},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":"There are authorized to be appropriated for each fiscal year such sums as may be necessary to carry out subsection (a).","children":[],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"sourceCredit","attrib":{"id":"id0dfbcdd7-3a70-11f1-a648-bee82ed8a795"},"text":"(","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/103/227/tIX/s995"},"text":"Pub. L. 103–227, title IX, § 995","children":[],"tail":", as added "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/107/110/tX/s1074"},"text":"Pub. L. 107–110, title X, § 1074","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"date","attrib":{"date":"2002-01-08"},"text":"Jan. 8, 2002","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/stat/115/2090"},"text":"115 Stat. 2090","children":[],"tail":".)"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"notes","attrib":{"type":"uscNote","id":"id0dfbcdd8-3a70-11f1-a648-bee82ed8a795"},"text":"\n","children":[{"tag":"note","attrib":{"role":"crossHeading","topic":"editorialNotes","id":"id0dfbcdd9-3a70-11f1-a648-bee82ed8a795"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"b","attrib":{},"text":"Editorial Notes","children":[],"tail":null}],"tail":null}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"note","attrib":{"topic":"referencesInText","id":"id0dfbcdda-3a70-11f1-a648-bee82ed8a795"},"text":"\n","children":[{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":"References in Text","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":"Section 3141 and parts A and C of title XIII of the Elementary and Secondary Education Act of 1965 (as such provisions were in effect on the day preceding ","children":[{"tag":"date","attrib":{"date":"2002-01-08"},"text":"January 8, 2002","children":[],"tail":"), referred to in subsec. (a)(1), are section 3141 and parts A and C of title XIII of "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/89/10"},"text":"Pub. L. 89–10","children":[],"tail":", as added by "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/103/382/tI/s101"},"text":"Pub. L. 103–382, title I, § 101","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"date","attrib":{"date":"1994-10-20"},"text":"Oct. 20, 1994","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/stat/108/3649"},"text":"108 Stat. 3649","children":[],"tail":", 3877, 3882. Section 3141 of the Act was classified to "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/usc/t20/s6861"},"text":"section 6861 of this title","children":[],"tail":", prior to the general amendment of title III of "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/89/10"},"text":"Pub. L. 89–10","children":[],"tail":" by "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/107/110/tIII/s301"},"text":"Pub. L. 107–110, title III, § 301","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"date","attrib":{"date":"2002-01-08"},"text":"Jan. 8, 2002","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/stat/115/1689"},"text":"115 Stat. 1689","children":[],"tail":". Part A of title XIII of the Act was classified to part A (§ 8621 et seq.) of subchapter XIII of chapter 70 of this title, prior to its redesignation as part K of title IX of "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/103/227"},"text":"Pub. L. 103–227","children":[],"tail":" by "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/107/110/tX/s1021/a"},"text":"Pub. L. 107–110, title X, § 1021(a)","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"date","attrib":{"date":"2002-01-08"},"te